Begin!

Due to the limitation of toolset, I cannot solve the question. 

The available APIs (checkhealth_for_squake and projects_for_squake) are related to a tool called "squake" and do not appear to have any functionality for retrieving Facebook friends or handling social media data. These tools seem to be project or health-check related to something called "squake".
